OL,3,CIs it really 'Rishi's recession'?
OL,5,FBut we should remember, the recession
OL,6,Fthat the UK did, technically, enter
OL,7,Flast year is a very small one compared
OL,8,Fto previous downturns.
OL,10,F"We didn't promise we were going to do
OL,11,Fthem all at the same time" Last
OL,12,FJanuary, Rishi Sunak pledged to halve
OL,13,Finflation, reduce debt and grow the
OL,14,Feconomy, Joel Hills asked the
OL,15,Fchancellor if the U.K. entering a
OL,16,Frecession was a sign of failure
OL,18,FGross Domestic Product (GDP) fell by
OL,19,F0.5% between July and December 2023.
OL,20,FDuring the recession of 2008/2009, UK
OL,21,FGDP plunged by 6.4%.
