OL,3,CIs it really 'Rishi's recession'?
OL,5,FHigher interest rates (not set by
OL,6,FRishi Sunak) have left households with
OL,7,Fmortgages poorer.
OL,9,FNeither strike action nor Brexit
OL,10,F(which Rishi Sunak can influence) have
OL,11,Fhelped.
OL,13,FNor has the fact that the UK workforce
OL,14,Fis smaller than it was before COVID,
OL,15,Fin part because there has been a sharp
OL,16,Frise in the number of people who
OL,17,Fcannot work because they are long-term
OL,18,Fsick.
